The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | The City Diary
                                                                                                               The City Diary
                An 18-year-old labourer died after he fell from the fourth floor of Vardaan Market, on Camac Street, on Monday. Mukaddar Rahaman, a resident of Malipanchghora in Howrah, was fitting aluminum windowpanes in an office when he lost his balance and fell. He was taken to a nursing home where he died in the afternoon. The body has been sent for post-mortem.    Three persons were injured when a speeding Matador hit a cyclevan on the eastern slope of Aurobindo Setu in Maniktala on Monday morning. Ratan Chakrabarty, Shambhu Roy and Raja Hari have been admitted to RG Kar Medical College and Hospital. The Matador driver fled without the vehicle.    An unidentified man in his 60s was seriously injured after being hit by a private bus (WBS 4848) at the Park Circus seven-point crossing around 7.30pm on Monday. He was admitted to National Medical College. Police said the bus sped away.    Manojit Ghorui, in his early-20s, was arrested in connection with wife Sunitas death early on Monday. Sunitas mother Snehalata said in her complaint that her daughter had attempted to hang herself from a ceiling fan last Tuesday after returning to her parents Duttabad home, beaten and bruised. Snehalata admitted Sunita at a nursing home in Phoolbagan, where she died.    About 300 residents of ARP Lane demonstrated at Shibpur police station on Monday demanding the arrest of promoter Sanjay Gupta, his aides Sanjay Thakur and Ramdhania Yadav, CPM leader Laxman Tiwari and four others. On Saturday, they had allegedly threatened to beat up residents of a slum if they refused to vacate the plot.     Abhishek Sharma, a 35-year-old auto driver, went missing on Saturday. Sharma is a resident of Behala.                                                                                                                                                                   
